    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) In Dei nomine amen. Millesimo centesimo quarto, indictione duodecima,
                        die dominico qui fuit sextus exeunte aprelis. Ego <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitissa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Countess #childOf #grandchildOf" ref="#people/125"
                            >Matilda</persName>, Dei gratia si quid sum, <rs key="#childOf"
                            >filia</rs> quondam <persName key="#Marquis/duke #parentOf"
                            ref="#people/1">Bonifatii</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionis</rs> tibi <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/2189">Alberico</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti
                            in Larione</orgName> nomine et vice eiusdem monasterii cui preesse
                        videris, quicquid pater et <rs key="#grandparentOf">avus</rs> meus <persName
                            key="#grandparentOf" ref="#people/2122">Tedaldus</persName> dederunt
                        predicto monasterio Sancti Benedicti in <placeName ref="#places/2959"
                            >Casalavone</placeName>, videlicet <rs>ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2074">Sancti Michaelis</orgName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/2936">Cotornione</placeName>, et alias
                        posessiones silicet <rs>casamenta</rs>, et <rs>agros</rs> et <rs>roncos de
                            bosco</rs> Casalavone, quod <geogFeat>nemus</geogFeat> est <rs>iuris
                            mei</rs>; et <rs>piscatores</rs> in <rs>paludibus</rs> illius terre,
                        duos aut tres et plus secundum voluntatem nuntii tui, per totum in integrum
                        concedo et confirmo in perpetuum, ut tu supradictus abbas et tui successores
                        habeas et teneas sine mea et heredum meorum contradictione. Et tibi hanc
                        potestatem concedo et tuis successoribus, pro anima mea et parentum meorum
                        ut nuncii tui, qui pro tempore fuerunt ibi, de predicto bosco et aliis
                        nemoribus illius terre roncare et boscare et pavolare et uti et frui
                        debeant, sine molestia et contradictione nostra et nostrorum ut supra
                        legitur; quam potestatem antecessores mei tuis antecessoribus dederunt.
                        Insuper quicquid monasterium tuum Sancti Benedicti in illa terra mea
                        aquirere vel lucrari poterit, cum mea licencia et heredum meorum facere
                        debeat; eo modo ut predictum monasterium Santi Benedicti habeat et teneat
                        omnia predicta cum omni honore et districtu et bannis. Actum est hoc in <rs
                            key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/145">Nogarie</placeName> feliciter,
                        presente <persName key="#Bishops #Witness">Ugone</persName>
                        <placeName>Mantue</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs>. Huius re <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count #Witness">Wido Guarra</persName>, comes <persName
                            key="#Count #Witness">Albertus</persName> filius
                            <persName>Bosonis</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                            >Arduinus</persName>, <persName>Gerardus</persName> filius
                            <persName>Bosonis</persName>, <persName>Ugo</persName> filius
                            <persName>Manfredi</persName>, <persName>Sasso</persName> et
                            <persName>Rainerius</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2468"
                            >Bibianello</placeName> et <persName>Lanfrancus</persName> et
                            <persName>Opizo</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2414"
                            >Gonzaga</placeName> et alii plures. (S.) Ego <persName
                            key="#Judge #Notary #Writer">Ubaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> hoc <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et dedi. </ab>
